data.title: Welcome to Dodge County, MN
data.text:
Natalie Webb Aquatic Center Location: 509 1st Ave NW, Dodge Center, MN 55927

Features: aquatic center with zero depth entry, toddler play area, water slides, two diving boards, lounge chairs, and concession stand.

For information on hours and fees, click HERE

Parks

Creek Park

Location: County Road 34 in Dodge Center - west of the Dodge Country Club

Features: rustic park without electricity or water, picnic shelter, bathrooms, two overnight RV spots, walking trail in the woods

North Park

Location: 604 North Central Ave, Dodge Center, MN 55927

Features: Cobra Country, large wooden castle play structure with multiple slides, bridges, swings, toddler play area, picnic shelter with bathrooms, water and electricity, two ball fields, tennis court, basketball court, soccer field, walking path with benches

Tall Oaks Park

Location: 106 South St SW, Dodge Center, MN 55927

Features: Small neighborhood park with playground equipment and benches

West Park

Location: 403 2nd St NW, Dodge Center, MN 55927

Features: picnic shelter with electricity, bathrooms with water and electricity, slide, swings, climbing structures, plentiful green space

Link to Dodge Center website HERE
